data.description: Stunning Stroud Township Colonial! 4 Bedroom, 2 1/2 Bath Home Offering Heated 2 Car Garage w/ Surround Sound & Freshly Finished Well-Lit Fully Equipped Basement For Entertaining & Relaxation. Eat-In Kitchen Has Granite Counters & Island, Newer Appliances & Deck Access. Spread Out w/ Your SPACIOUS Formal Dining Room, Family Room & Living Rooms. Primary Bedroom Suite Showcases Renovated Bath w/ Heated Flooring & Large Closet. Exterior Features Desirable Cul-De-Sac Setting On 1 Acre Tree-Lined Lot w/ Storage Shed, Long Paved Driveway & Expansive Tiered Deck Overlooking Private Backyard Paradise w/ Fire-Pit & Geodesic Canopy Gazebo Backing Up To Beautiful Countryside Forest. No Dues Stroudsburg School District Location Close-To-Town, Shopping, Medical Facilities & Major Routes. Made You Look!
